getPushResult

IPushResult getPushResult(java.lang.String taskId)
获取推送任务编号为指定taskId的推送结果数据。(如：发送数，点击数，接受数等)
Get the details of push result (Such as how many sent, how many user clicked, and how many feedback). only offer toList and toApp tasks, single message is not support.

参数：
taskId - 任务ID
返回：
The push result contains:
  • result - ok or failed
  • msgTotal - the count of message sent
  • msgProcess - the count of feedback

    queryAppPushDataByDate

    IQueryResult queryAppPushDataByDate(java.lang.String appId,
                                    java.lang.String date)
    通过日期，获取App维度的推送数据
    Get app push data by date

    参数：
    appId -
    date - 格式 ： yyyyMMdd
    返回：
    The result contains:
  • result - ok or failed
  • data.newRegistCount - the count for new regist user
  • data.registTotalCount - the total for regist user
  • data.activeCount - the count for active user
  • data.onlineCount - the count for online user

    • queryAppUserDataByDate

    IQueryResult queryAppUserDataByDate(java.lang.String appId,
                                    java.lang.String date)
    通过日期，获取App维度的用户数据
    Get app user data by date

    参数：
    appId -
    date - 格式 ： yyyyMMdd
    返回：
    The result contains:
  • result - ok or failed
  • data.sendCount - the count message to send, include online and offline message
  • data.sendOnlineCount - the count message to send, only include online message
  • data.receiveCount - the count to receive
  • data.showCount - the count to display notification
  • data.clickCount - the count to click notification
